title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 8/29 - 13 Reasons, Anthony LaPanta
description: In honor of the season opener being 13 days away, PA & Nordo give 13 reasons why the Vikings will beat the Packers week 1.  Wild TV play-by-play voice Anthony LaPanta joins the show to discuss all the latest with the WIld!
